s0">about Him. </div><div class="t m0 x1f h1d yff ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jagga<span class="ws1cf">ya asked a Protestant pastor in his village to tell him more about</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y22 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws4d">Jesus. Soon Jagg<span class="ws0">a<span class="ws6f0">ya was attending church and reading his Bible. Al<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws0">w<span class="_ _2"></span>ays</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y100 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his pray<span class="ws6f1">er was that Jesus would teach him more. Then one day a stranger</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y23 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">walked into Jagg<span class="_ _1"></span>a<span class="_ _2"></span>ya’s village. </div><div class="t m0 x1f h1d ye7 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paul Reddy pra<span class="_ _2"></span>y<span class="ws5a1">ed as he neared the village, “Lord, lead me to some soul</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y24 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws54e">longing to know more about <span class="_ _2"></span><span class="ws0">Y<span class="_ _15"></span>ou.<span class="_ _2"></span>”<span class="_ _d"> </span><span class="ws4ae">As he walked down the street, he</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d ye8 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws3cd">noticed an old man reading a Bible. “Hello, Brother<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws0">,<span class="_ _2"></span><span class="ws6f2">” Paul greeted the</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y25 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws4ea">man. “I see you are reading God’<span class="_ _e"></span><span class="ws0">s<span class="_ _4"> </span>W<span class="_ _2"></span><span class="ws5d9">ord. I am a Christian too.<span class="_ _2"></span><span class="ws0">”<span class="_ _1b"> </span>The two</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d ye9 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws6f3">men talked for a while, then Paul asked him, “Do you know about the</div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y26 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible Sabbath?” </div>