pan>w<span class="_ _2"></span>ed what he had learned from Paul Reddy and the</div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d yef ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible. </div><div class="t m0 x1f h1d yf0 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jagga<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws19b">ya is 80 years old, but he walks the streets of his village sharing</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d yf1 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws3ce">his newfound faith with others. He is studying the Bible with 20 people he</div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d yf2 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws432">has found. They are preparing to be baptized into the Adventist church. </div><div class="t m0 x1f h1d y104 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws6f7">The work in Orissa State in eastern India is exploding. In 1997 after 70</div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y105 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">y<span class="ws121">ears of Adventist work, the church had 102 congre</span>g<span class="ws154">ations in Orissa and</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y106 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3,100 belie<span class="_ _1"></span>vers. <span class="_ _1"></span>T<span class="_ _2"></span><span class="ws550">oday there are more than 350 congre<span class="ws0">g<span class="ws2a4">ations and more</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y14 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">than 30,000 believ<span class="_ _0"></span>ers. Pray that God will open the w<span class="_ _2"></span>a<span class="_ _0"></span>y to build more than</div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y164 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws6f8">300 churches needed by new congre<span class="ws0">g<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws4cb">ations in Orissa. Pray too that our</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h1d y165 ff9a fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 wsa7">new members will remain faithful to God in spite of great dif<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws0">f<span class="_ _1"></span>iculties.</span></div><div class="t m0 x2c h2a y20a ff99 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dorothy Eaton <span class="_ _0"></span>W<span class="_ _e"></span>atts is assistant secr